{"tid":163391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"30歲男觀塘墮樓喪命 母哭斷腸","createTime":"2017-03-20T02:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T01:27:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95501fc5a45cc79e179d15bb338bd82bbbae0a0c","tid":163391,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n凌晨約3時25分，觀塘道448至458號官塘工業中心，一名姓黃30歲男子在2、3期之間走廊高處墮下，倒臥地上昏迷，保安員發現報警。救護員接報到場，將墮樓男子送院搶救，證實不治。母親及家人趕抵醫院，母親聞悉兒子死訊傷心痛哭。警方現場沒有撿獲遺書，初步諣調查無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56452376&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56452376%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170320&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=6931e9a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56452376%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170320&h=7db305a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56452376&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170320</a>"},{"pid":"f31e3528e843cbed30796dc3dfa1115b97fbf377","tid":163391,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:50:48.000Z","msg":"咁多人自殺"},{"pid":"3ff7e1f6b26f2a981b7474b35f19fc6ca371e59e","tid":163391,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"週圍空中飛人，好多有情緒病"},{"pid":"0f5644f0bb72982d6168533d2068f87604f8def3","tid":163391,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:52: